# Scripted REST API

Endpoint:
POST /api/x_<scope>_hr_sec_lite/hr_conf_req_api/create

## Security Logic
- Only HR agent/admin roles allowed
- Non-authorized users receive 403 Forbidden

## Payload Example

{
  "title": "Update dependent information",
  "description": "Need to update beneficiary",
  "requested_for": "sys_id_here"
}

## Admin-only Field
SSN last4 can only be set if caller has admin role.
